---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="SRP Portfolio - frontpage">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section id="hero" class="container mx-auto text-center py-20">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-gray-100 tracking-wider pt-32">Hey there!</h1>
    <h2 class="font-medium text-gray-400 mt-4 tracking-widest">Welcome to my portfolio</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-6 leading-7 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      Specialising in UX- and web-design, I’m a designer passionate about crafting accessible and user-friendly digital experiences. With a strong
      foundation in both coding and design, I strive to create visually engaging platforms that prioritize clean, functional, and inclusive solutions
      for all users.
    </p>
    <a
      href="#projects"
      class="relative z-[1] text-gray-100 bg-site-red font-bold rounded-lg text-sm px-6 py-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden group mt-8 transition duration-300 uppercase"
    >
      <span class="relative z-[1] w-full text-center uppercase">View projects</span>
      <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-700 transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0"></span>
    </a>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <div class="bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-70 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100">About me</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 leading-7">
          As a multimedia-designer, I specialize in UX and web design, with a strong focus on accessibility and inclusive design. I have a deep
          understanding of the meaning of design, its impact on usability, and the overall importance of creating visually engaging and user-friendly
          interfaces. As someone who's late-diagnosed with autism, I know what it's like to be a person who's not fully capable of certain things and
          have limited understanding of the world around them. This has led me to my main goal&mdash; to create digital experiences that are
          accessible and inclusive for all users, regardless of their disabilities.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 leading-7">
          Creativity is at the heart of everything I do, driving me to explore the world of design with enthusiasm and curiosity. Each project
          presents a chance to transform ideas into meaningful experiences that connect with others. I thrive on the excitement of experimenting with
          new techniques and discovering innovative ways to bring concepts to life. As I journey through this ever-evolving field, I look forward to
          embracing new challenges and forging connections that inspire growth and creativity. The future holds endless possibilities, and I'm eager
          to see where this path will lead me.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
        <img src="images/pfp.webp" alt="About Me Image" class="w-[350px] h-[350px] rounded-full shadow-md object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

